8. Redlib Health: Fixed issue where Portainer reported 'Unhealthy' due to 403 errors (while dashboard correctly showed 'Online'). Updated healthcheck to ignore 403s.
9. Update Engine: Added manual 'Check for Updates' button and backend logic.
10. Master Update: Added a permanent 'Update All Services' button that triggers both global image updates (Watchtower) and source code refreshes.
11. Material Design 3: Verified full compliance with M3 tokens (color, shape, motion), expressive elevations, and typography.

DASHBOARD COG FUNCTIONALITY:
==========================================================
The settings cog triggers a Service Modal providing:
- Real-time CPU/Memory metrics for the specific container.
- Individual "Update Service" button (Source pull + Rebuild).
- "View in Portainer" deep link to the container ID.
- Specialized maintenance buttons (Migrate DB, Clear Logs, Optimize DB).